--- !u!1001 &642928761
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 1186717341}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mNPCName
      value: Blacksmith
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mTextBox
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1111739680}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mTextAnimator
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1040579190}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: mDialogue.Array.size
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[0]'
      value: Hey Pit!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[1]'
      value: I'm really busy today.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[2]'
      value: So I prepared three tools you might need today.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[3]'
      value: You'll just need to feed some materials into the machines behind my
        house.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[4]'
      value: You'll need iron for a sword to cut down vegetation.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[5]'
      value: One wood to create a stick to grab items far away.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[6]'
      value: And a crystal to create a spyglass to identify far away items.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[7]'
      value: They all should be nearby, try near the cliffs for the iron.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'mDialogue.Array.data[8]'
      value: The wood near the forest.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3498568096948360507, guid: ea4164403dcef01459d0233e3cccc085, type: 3}
